===============================================================================
                               VIM SETUP
===============================================================================

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Link VSCode folder from repo root
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ln -s "$(pwd)/vim/.vimrc" \
      "$HOME/.vimrc"

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check LST config (inside VIM)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
:CocConfig

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install pylance LSP (inside VIM)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
:CocInstall coc-pyright

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install cpp clang LSP (inside VIM)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
:CocInstall coc-clangd

===============================================================================
